									<span class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://www.washingtonsblog.com/general" title="View all posts in General" rel="category tag">General</a>					</span>
					<span class="meta-sep">|</span>
												<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://www.washingtonsblog.com/2014/07/sign-amnesty-intl-petition-urge-u-s-government-stop-arming-israel.html#comments" title="Comment on Sign Amnesty Int&#8217;l Petition to &#8220;Urge U.S. Government to stop arming Israel&#8221;"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="33864 http://www.washingtonsblog.com/?p=33864">3 Comments</span></a></span>
